thread.title: Sooper Yooper
thread.title_full: Frames Direct reviewed by Sooper Yooper

author: Sooper Yooper
title: Sooper Yooper
text: Very pleased with the frames - very sturdy. I'd had my previous Titmus safety glasses for about 12 years so the lens clarity was pronounced. The placement of the bi-focal was perfect - not easy when the client isn't present with the lens tech for an accurate measurement.
